title: Lawful Money Held, National Banks, Country Districts for United States
notes:
Data Were Computed By NBER By Summing "Specie", "Legal Tender Notes", And "U.S. Certificates Of Deposit" Whenever Given Separately. Monthly Coverage Varies From Year To Year. Except For 1874, Which Only Has Data For October And December, All Years Have Scattered Five Month Coverage. Source: Computed By NBER From Annual Reports Of The Comptroller Of The Currency.

This NBER data series m14011 appears on the NBER website in Chapter 14 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter14.html.
